- Treating missing values¶

Predicting the missing values¶

Here, we try to predict the missing values using a regressor. First we split the dataset into two parts- one that contains the missing values in the target variable and the other that doesn't. Next we train our model on the dataset that does not have any missing values, and use that model to then predict the missing values
